source.name: Small & Medium-Sized Exporting Companies: Statistical Overview
source.description: This overview outlines the export activities of U.S. Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises (SMEs). Data presented here are generated from the U.S. Commerce Department's Exporter Database (EDB).
